These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-1::.
House: gothic-revival, palace, ranch-style, cape-cod, farmhouse, craftsman, cottage
The people have 7 different hobbies: puzzles, baking, sudoku, photography, filmmaking, fishing, chess
 1. the person who's hobby is chess is the cape-cod house##1
 2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not to the left of the ranch-style house##8
 3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##8
 4. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
 5. the gothic-revival house is not to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##8
 6. the gothic-revival house is not the person who's hobby is baking##6
 7. the farmhouse house is in an odd position##4
 8. the farmhouse house is not to the left of the cottage house##8
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's hobby is baking##7
10. the person who's hobby is baking is the craftsman house##1
11. the craftsman house is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the cottage house##1
14. the cottage house is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is puzzles##7
15. the craftsman house is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
16. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the farmhouse house##8
17. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the left of the gothic-revival house##5
18. the cottage house is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
19. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
20. the cape-cod house is not the person who's hobby is fishing##6
21. the gothic-revival house is not to the right of the gothic-revival house##8
22. the palace house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |      3       |    4    |    5     |      6      |    7    |
| House           | craftsman | ranch-style | cottage | palace  | farmhouse  | cape-cod | gothic-revival    |
| Hobby   | baking   | puzzles   | sudoku   | photography | filmmaking | chess        | fishing |

