 4. the american is between the indian and the person watching time-travel movies##2
 5. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an odd position##4
 6. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the turkish##1
 7. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
 8. the argentine is not to the left of the turkish##8
