11. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
12. the chinese is not to the right of the turkish##8
13. the person watching western movies is not to the left of the person watching family movies##8
14. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the mexican##5
15. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the turkish##3
16. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
