 3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person eating lime##1
 4. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
 5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 6. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 7. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the person eating cabbage##5
 8. the person eating lemon is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
 9. the owner of the pony is in the middle##1
10. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the person eating raspberry##5
11. the person eating asparagus is in an even position##4
12. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the horse##2
13. the owner of the pony is not the person eating lime##6
14. the person eating asparagus is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5

.:: Answer ::.
